---

<Layout
  title="Portfolio | Tấn Đạt"
  description="Portfolio của Tấn Đạt - ứng tuyển vị trí AI Engineer / Machine Learning Engineer."
>
  <Header />

  <main id="main-content" class="relative min-h-screen">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="portfolio-page-bg"></div>
    </div>

    <section class="reveal-block relative overflow-hidden border-b border-border is-visible">
      <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_20%_20%,rgba(37,99,235,0.12),transparent_40%),radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_10%,rgba(37,99,235,0.08),transparent_40%)]"></div>
      <div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-10 px-6 py-18 sm:py-24 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_0.7fr] lg:items-center">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="reveal-up mb-5 inline-flex rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-accent" style="--reveal-delay: 0.05s;">
            Open to Internship / Fresher Opportunities
          </p>

          <h1 class="reveal-up max-w-4xl text-4xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl" style="--reveal-delay: 0.15s;">
            Hi, mình là Tấn Đạt.
            <span class="block text-accent">Machine Learning Engineer Portfolio.</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="reveal-up mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground" style="--reveal-delay: 0.25s;">
            Mình tập trung vào ML, CV, MLOps và Data Engineering, với định hướng triển khai dự án end-to-end.
          </p>

          <div class="reveal-up mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3" style="--reveal-delay: 0.35s;">
            <a href="#projects" class="rounded-md bg-accent px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-background shadow-[0_10px_20px_rgba(8,86,159,0.24)] transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:opacity-95">
              Xem dự án nổi bật
            </a>
            <a href="/cv" class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background/85 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-accent hover:text-accent">
              Xem CV
            </a>
            <a href="/learning-path" class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background/85 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-accent hover:text-accent">
              Vào Blog học tập
            </a>
            <a href="#contact" class="rounded-md border border-border bg-background/85 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold transition hover:border-accent hover:text-accent">
              Liên hệ phỏng vấn
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal-up mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs" style="--reveal-delay: 0.45s;">
            <span class="rounded-full border border-accent/25 bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-accent">Computer Vision</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-accent/25 bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-accent">MLOps</span>
            <span class="rounded-full border border-accent/25 bg-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-accent">Data Engineering</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-sm animate-profile-in hero-float">
